Description: Your Search for a smart and compact digital thermometer ends here, as the Operon TS-8 I Care 3 in 1 Digital Thermometer has been designed to suit all your temperature based requirements. This user friendly device is clubbed with a 3 in 1 function of taking the ear, forehead and ambient temperatures, facilitating an easy measurement of your body and room temperature. Apart from being a three in one functioning device, this digital thermometer also provides  instant temperature results without having to spend a lot of time on measuring your temperature. Body This easily portable Operon TS-8 I Care 3 in 1 Digital Thermometer comes with a large LCD display that provides easy readability, most importantly for the elders. The easy- to- clean digital thermometer from Operon comes with a probe cover sealing it away from dust and grime thus facilitating easy maintenance. Features This smartly designed Operon TS-8 I Care 3 In 1 Digital Thermometer comes with a low battery indicator which alerts you when your battery is low, thereby saving power. The Auto Power Off Function automatically turns off the power in the thermometer after it is in an idle mode for more than a minute, ensuring battery durability. The measuring accuracy for ear ranges from 95.9 degree Fahrenheit  - 107.6 degree Fahrenheit and forehead temperature ranges from 71.6 degree Fahrenheit - 104 degree Fahrenheit. The operating environment temperature of this digital thermometer ranges from 60.8 degree Fahrenheit t - 95 degree Fahrenheit.  This technically advanced digital thermometer from Operon is also embedded with a Fever Alarm which gives you a signal when your temperature is high. The device consists of one 3.OV CR-2032 battery. Versatile and effortless- to- use this Operon multifunctional device is a safe option for detecting temperature.
